15. Enter the 6-digit verification code
16. Click the Verify button to continue
You will receive a message saying your
email has been verified.

On the Dashboard
17. Click the Link icon to connect your
cafeteria account

18. Enter the following information:
• School ID
• Select your School
• Last Name
19. Click the Find My Cafeteria Account button
to link your SchoolCafé account with your
Cafeteria ID account
If you cannot find your cafeteria account,
contact your nutrition office.
